            </a:pPr>
            <a:r>
              <a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="3200" b="1" dirty="0"/>
              <a:t>3. DISPATCH — Nearest available drone auto-assigned with optimal routing and live airspace constraints. 4. RESPOND — HD aerial feed + GPS pushed to responders in real-time. 5. RESOLVE — Drone maintains on-scene situational awareness until ground teams arrive.</a:t>
            </a:r>
          </a:p>
          <a:p>
