              <a:t>GPS reliability in urban canyons → Multi-sensor fusion (GPS + IMU + visual odometry). No-fly zone compliance → Pre-loaded airspace constraints with dynamic rerouting. Battery range limits → Staggered charging; 12km average coverage per charge. False positive alerts → Two-stage AI verification reduces false alarms to under 0.8%.</a:t>
